rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0001
rows.name:
What could this building have been for?
It seems to have lots of shelves for
storing things...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0002
rows.name: This looks like a pipe organ...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0003
rows.name: But it's not making any sound now...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0101
rows.name:
These shelves are perfectly spaced for
climbing... No! I have to resist the urge!

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0103
rows.name:
Oh, but it's busted... Shame,
I wanted to play a little tune.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0201
rows.name:
Meh-meh! This building so big!
Is big mansion for royal people maybe?

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0203
rows.name:
Some things same here as in world
of Tora and friends...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0301
rows.name:
This place seems almost like a gigantic
market. Did people gather here to trade
goods long ago?

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0302
rows.name:
The organ... How majestic it must have
sounded, before...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0401
rows.name:
What're these things? Shelves?
I guess it's some kind of shop.

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0402
rows.name:
But what the heck kind of shop is
bigger than our royal throne room...?

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0403
rows.name: Hm, no go. Won't make a sound...

rows.label: tlk00000592_01_msg0404
rows.name:
Sad, really. If it was still working,
I could have given everyone a taste of
the Zekenator's Fifth...
